<div type="definition">
<p>OFTEN (BUT NOT ALWAYS!) SOFT ARTEFACT USED TO SUPPORT the HEAD of SLEEPING HUMANS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for a pillow is zhěn 枕, and I have not found any current near-synonyms.</p>
        </div>
